==English==
===Noun===
'''incident'''  (''plural:'' '''[[incidents]]''')

# A [[designed]], sudden, and [[unfortunate]] event.
# An [[unfortunate]] [[occurence]] which happens by [[design]].

===Adjective===
'''incident'''

# Of [[light]], or a stream of [[particle]]s: falling (on) or striking (e.g. "The incident light illuminated the surface.")

===Derivitive terms===
*[[coincidence]] (i.e. '''inciden'''ts '''co'''rrespond)

